[[File:Jashar Pasha mosque.jpg|thumb|120x240px|Jashar Pasha Mosque]] The '''Jashar Pasha Mosque''' is a Mosque in [[Pristina|Prishtina]], [[Kosovo]].<ref name = J.Pasha>{{cite web|last=Drançolli|first=Fejaz|title=Jashar Pasha Mosque|url=http://www.seecorridors.eu/filebank/file_176.pdf|location=Pristina|date=11.03.2004}}</ref> It was named after [[Mehmet Yasar]].<ref name = K.guide>{{cite book|last=Balla|first=Shefqet|title=Kosova Guide|publisher=abs books, www.abs.com|isbn=978-9951-8780-4-3}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Warrander|first=Gail|title=Kosovo|publisher=Bradt Travel Guides Ltd, UK|isbn=978-1-84162-331-3|url=http://www.bradtguides.com/|author2=Verena Knaus}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Një e ardhme për të kaluarën e Pishtinës|url=http://www.esiweb.org/pdf/esi_future_of_pristina%20booklet_albanian.pdf|publisher=Kosova Stability Initiative, European Stability Initiative|accessdate=23 February 2014|language=Albanian}}</ref>
