'''Matsieng Air Strip''' {{Airport codes||FBMA}} is a new (built in 2011) [[general aviation]] airport near [[Rasesa]], {{convert|44|km}} north of [[Gaborone]], [[Botswana]].
The airport has served as a venue for several international air shows.<ref name="fnb">{{cite web|title=2015 Botswana International Air Show|url=https://www.fnbbotswana.co.bw/news/archive/2015/11052015International-Air-Show.html|website=First National Bank Botswana|accessdate=8 May 2017}}</ref><ref name="pp">{{cite web|last1=Keyter|first1=Juri|title=Wesbank Botswana International Air Show 2016|url=http://pilotspost.com/arn0000983|website=Pilotspost|accessdate=8 May 2017}}</ref><ref name="ba">{{cite web|title=2017 Botswana International Air Show|url=http://www.botswana-airshow.com/index.php/fly-in-camping|website=Botswana Airshow|accessdate=8 May 2017}}</ref>
