{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2012}} {{Infobox diocese |jurisdiction = Archdiocese |name = Kupang |latin = Archidioecesis Kupangensis |local = Keuskupan Agung Kupang |country = {{flag|Indonesia}} |rite = [[Latin Rite]] |province = Kupang |cathedral = Cathedral of Christ the King in [[Kupang]] |cocathedral = |area_km2 = 11,285 |population = 1,189,829 |population_as_of = 2004 |catholics = 125,123 |catholics_percent= 10.5 |pope = {{Incumbent pope}} |metro_archbishop = [[Peter Turang]] |coadjutor = |auxiliary_bishops= }}
The '''Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Kupang''' ({{lang-la|Kupangensis}}) is an [[archdiocese]] located in the city of [[Kupang]], [[East Nusa Tenggara]] province in [[Indonesia]].
==History== * 13 April 1967: Established as Diocese of Kupang from the [[Diocese of Atambua]] * 23 October 1989: Promoted as Metropolitan Archdiocese of Kupang
==Leadership== * Arch[[bishop]]s of Kupang (Roman rite) ** Archbishop Peter Turang (10 October 1997 – present) ** Archbishop [[Gregorius Manteiro]], [[S.V.D.]] (23 October 1989 – 10 October 1997) * Bishops of Kupang (Roman Rite) ** Bishop Gregorius Manteiro, S.V.D. (later Archbishop) (13 April 1967 – 23 October 1989)
==Suffragan dioceses== * [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Atambua|Atambua]] * [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Weetebula|Weetebula]]
